Pre-reqs
--------

* Make sure your your distros base channel is enabled (rhel-7-server-rpms on RHEL7, base on CentOS7)
* Make sure the hostname is resolveable
* Upload the jon zip file(s) to /tmp
* This git repo needs to be cloned to /root for now
* Internet access

Tested on el7.

Installation
------------

# git clone https://github.com/opuk/jon-all-in-one.git
# cd jon-all-in-one
# ./runme.sh

Troubleshooting
---------------

1. Poke hole in the firewall as needed.
2. You may need to adjust some of the variables in the applyme.pp file.
